creator: Viditure.inc
descriptionHtml:
Digital Invea is a one stop medium for all your Ethiopian passport, origin ID and Lasse Passer related services for Ethiopian diaspora. this Application allows the users to apply for new and renewal of their passport, Origin ID and Lesser Passer.
Digital Invea provides a secure way to provide necessary details, upload the appropriate documents, conduct the payment, and apply for new and renewal services(of Passport and Origin ID) with few clicks that takes 5 to 10 minutes. All applications will be processed within a secured administrative panel at INVIA centralized office. This reform will convert the manual and time consuming documentation processing into a robust online process via digital technology.
